bug.short_desc: The loading toolbar is shown over the horizontal scroll

assigned_to.name: Nobody; OK to take it and work on it

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 524368 loading toolbar issue
Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; rv:2.2a1pre) Gecko/20110406 Firefox/4.2a1pre
When the horizontal scroll is present, the loading toolbar is shown over it.
Steps to reproduce: 1. Set the screen resolution to 800x600 2. Go to www.realitatea.net 3. Make sure that the horizontal scroll is present
Actual Results: The toolbar is shown over the horizontal scroll (see screenshot)
Expected Results: The toolbar should be shown above the horizontal scroll
*** This bug has been marked as a duplicate of bug 629907 ***
